Author: belivets
Text: god self awareness is the WORST. like, the logical part of my brain is screaming at me sometimes, like *WHY are upset over that "binge" when it was just a normal, average sized lunch eaten at an appropriate time?* but then the e. dpart of my brain like *sandwich.... bad??? NO food later...*  every now and again one of them hits the other with a stick and things are chill for a bit. until they eventually start up again, like my brain are two unruly children and i am their long suffering day drinking mom.
